:section-start "Intro"
:bodytext
"Having a modular way to divide the pitch continuum - the octave - has demonstrated to be a powerful tool for study and control the pitch relations."
:bodytext"In the rhythm domain there is not such a natural way of dividing the continuum and therefore, any attempt of study the rhythmic relations becomes a more difficult task."
:bodytext"Still there are some ways to control the relations between rhythmic designs and hence, use them for analysis and composition."

:section-end